Package: soilVAE
Type: Package
Title: Supervised Variational Autoencoder (VAE) for Soil Spectroscopy Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hugo", family = "Rodrigues",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rodrigues.machado.hugo@gmail.com")
Description: Tools to build, tune, and use a supervised variational autoencoder (VAE)
    regression model for soil spectroscopy and related high-dimensional predictors.
    The model is implemented in Python (Keras 3 / TensorFlow) and accessed from R via reticulate.
